f2(x,y)=min{f2(x−1,y),f2(x−1,y−1)}+triangle[x][y]f_2(x,y) = min\{f_2(x-1, y), f_2(x-1, y-1)\} + triangle[x][y]f​2​​(x,y)=min{f​2​​(x−1,y),f​2​​(x−1,y−1)}+triangle[x][y]
